#Spacetime Plaza - Master File (For entire complex)
#Copyright (c) 2026-Present - Mn10

#Started on: 30 April 2026 (Idea originated around April-May 2017.)

#Notes about this place:
	#General:
	#1. Restrooms will be added as I work more on this place.
	#2. Not all parking ramps have been created yet.
	#3. As of 13 May 2026, only the parking spaces on this complex's easternmost side have been completed.
	#4. More entrance doors would come as I progress more.
	#5. I apologize if the escalators' undersides lower the "clearance" on some areas of level B1.
		# At least, the clearance is still high enough for standard vehicles that I don't have to convert certain parking areas to be storage or utility (like on level 4A of Bell Nature Mall or level 5A of Destiny Plaza).
		# NOTE: Parking garages IRL typically contains some more things in the ceilings (such as pipes, beams, and lights), not just the escalators' undersides.
	#6. Walls and windows covering the elevator/escalator lobbies on B2-B1 will be created later on.
	#7. As the escalators are only available in the floor mesh, they will disappear upon walking to another engine (such as between April DS and the main mall).

	#All shopping zones (Main mall, April DS, and Monica DS):
	#1. Not all escalators have been created yet.
	#2. The "East Annex" will be completed later on.
	#3. Please use your imagination for the "support columns" on all shopping levels. I can't always add every little detail for every building of mine.

	#Main mall:
	#1. Elevators 16-21 and 24-27 will not be used by the "random people" at all. This could be changed in Skyscraper Simulator's future updates.
	#2. On the 8th floor, there is not any wall south of Stairwell 6 as that area will be a storage.
	#3. Railings in the South Zone (the 4-story annex west of April DS) will be created later.

	#Monica Department Store:
	#1. This area is not intended to have its own service/freight elevators.
	#2. A second stairwell will come later.
	#3. Not all atrium railings have been completed yet.

